race.comment: Tough. SUGOI LEGEND (6) steps back up to this trip and that suits. His middle-distance form prior to the synthetic outing read strongly for this contest. Maps well and the 2kg claim is handy. DOONICAN (9) was plainer back to a mile last time but his form this distance range is also strong for this contest. He just missed at Launceston three back and has been kept up to the mark with a Longford trial. Go well. DYNAMIC DEEL (2) lifted from a mile and missed by 1.7L at Launceston. In the mix on that effort. I'M CHEV (7) is better on the synthetic but would be around the mark putting his best foot forward.
